head
  title Reviving the Dream of the 90s
  meta( charset='utf-8' )
  meta( name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1' http-equiv='Content-Type' )
  link( href='https://unpkg.com/normalize.css@8.0.0/normalize.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' )
  link( href='style.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' )
  meta( property='og:title' content='Reviving the Dream of the 90s with WebGL' )
  meta( property='og:description' content='Recreating screensavers with modern web technology to bring back some of that exuberant 90s energy.' )
  meta( property='og:image' content='https://billyroh.com/screensavers/assets/social-maze.jpg' )
  meta( property='og:image:width' content='2400' )
  meta( property='og:image:height' content='1260' )
  meta( property='og:url' content='https://billyroh.com/screensavers' )
  meta( property='og:type' content='website' )
body
  .top-bar-wrapper
    .blue-bar
      .left-content
        .icon.app-icon
          img( src='./assets/paint-brush.ico' )
        .title Reviving the Dream of the 90s with WebGL
      .right-content.blue-bar-buttons
        .button: .icon: img( src='./assets/minimize.svg' )
        .button: .icon: img( src='./assets/maximize.svg' )
        .button: .icon: img( src='./assets/close.svg' )
    .action-bar
      .action
        span.action-underline F
        | ile
      .action
        span.action-underline E
        | dit
      .action
        span.action-underline V
        | iew
  .viewport
    section
      img.header( src='./assets/header.png' )
      p The 90s were an exuberant time for the technology that we take for granted today. This is an attempt to bring back some of that energy by recreating 90s screensavers with WebGL and other modern web technologies.
      p
        | Special thanks to&nbsp;
        a( href='https://twitter.com/visnup' ) Visnu Pitiyanuvath
        | &nbsp;for all his help with this.
      .section-button-wrapper
        a.button( href='https://github.com/billyroh/screensavers' ) View Source
        a.button( href='' ) See Slides
    section
      a( href='./pipes' ): video( src='./assets/pipes.mp4' autoplay loop muted playsinline )
      h3 Pipes
      p On desktop, use WASD and your cursor to move and pan around. You can also change the colour palette.
      a.button( href='./pipes' ) View Pipes
    section
      a( href='./maze' ): video( src='./assets/maze.mp4' autoplay loop muted playsinline )
      h3 Maze
      p Get the authentic NYC experience by adding more rats with the buttons at the bottom.
      a.button( href='./maze' ) View Maze
    section
      a( href='./matrix' ): video( src='./assets/matrix.mp4' autoplay loop muted playsinline )
      h3 The Matrix
      p Try changing the language options, as well as the colour palette.
      a.button( href='./matrix' ) View the Matrix
  .bottom-bar-wrapper
    .menu-bar-delineator
    .menu-bar
      .left-content
        .start-button.button
          .icon: img( src='./assets/windows-logo.ico' )
          span Start
        .menu-bar-item
          .icon: img( src='./assets/paint-brush.ico' )
          span.menu-bar-item-text Reviving the Dream of the 90s with WebGL
      .right-content
        .time
  script( src='scripts.js' )
